verbs.description: Network and cable channels could n’t get enough of Michael Avenatti , granting Stormy Daniels’ personal attorney a whopping 162 interviews in the past 12 weeks ( March 7 through May 30 ) . But those outlets are now going to have to find a new pundit to embarrass Donald Trump with , as the judge presiding over the porn star ’s case against former Trump personal attorney Michael Cohen
